<HEAD>
<TITLE>CDT Policy Post 2.32 - FBI Surveillance Demands Rejected on Privacy Grounds</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<PRE>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    _____ _____ _______
   / ____|  __ \__   __|   ____        ___               ____             __
  | |    | |  | | | |     / __ \____  / (_)______  __   / __ \____  _____/ /_
  | |    | |  | | | |    / /_/ / __ \/ / / ___/ / / /  / /_/ / __ \/ ___/ __/
