14.        shall not apply where the good faith defense under<br>
15.        subsection (c)(2) apply.<br>
16.        "(6) No state or local governmnet may impose<br>
17.        any liability in connection with a violation described<br>
18.        in subsection (a)(2), (b)(1)(B), (b)(2)(B) that is in-<br>
19.        consistent with the treatment of those violations<br>
20.        under this section provided, however, that nothing<br>
21.        herein shall preclude any State or local governmnet<br>
22.        from enacting and enforcing complementary over-<br>
23.        sight, liability, and regulatory systems, procedures,<br>
24.        and requirements, so long as such systems, proce-<br>
25.        dures and requirements govern only interstate serv-<br>
<p>
