<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001029-B017-224</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdt.org:80/crypto/960502_Burns_stmnt.html 205.177.10.31 19970215020030 text/html 8001
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 01:59:14 GMT
