<HEAD>
<TITLE>CDT Policy Post 2.33 - FTC Recommends Changes to Protect Personal Info</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<PRE>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    _____ _____ _______
   / ____|  __ \__   __|   ____        ___               ____             __
