<HEAD>
<TITLE>CDT Policy Post 2.38 - President Takes First Steps Towards Clipper 3.1.1</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFFF>
<PRE>
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    _____ _____ _______
   / ____|  __ \__   __|   ____        ___               ____             __
  | |    | |  | | | |     / __ \____  / (_)______  __   / __ \____  _____/ /_
  | |    | |  | | | |    / /_/ / __ \/ / / ___/ / / /  / /_/ / __ \/ ___/ __/
  | |____| |__| | | |   / ____/ /_/ / / / /__/ /_/ /  / ____/ /_/ (__  ) /_
