<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdt.org:80/crypto/current_legis/960626_Zimm_test.html 205.177.10.31 19970215022305 text/html 18557
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 02:21:46 GMT
