<DOCNO>WT02-B06-138</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001029-B019-54</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cdt.org:80/crypto/plewis.html 205.177.10.31 19970215020557 text/html 9038
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 02:04:41 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
